HEADWORD: confusing
<hw>confusing</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>causing mental
confusion and perplexity.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> perplexing, stupefying.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>causing bafflement and confusion; <as>as, he sent
